# [MAILMAINT](../wg/mailmaint.html)

## Summary
The MAILMAINT Working Group met at IETF 126 in Vienna to discuss the progress of its active drafts. Key topics included interoperability testing updates for OAuth and PACC, outstanding design and deployment issues for Mail Autoconfig, proposed Unicode constraint rules for SMTPUTF8 syntax, schema design and tombstone mechanisms for Personal Data Portability (PDP) Archive, transport-related signature breakage in Unobtrusive Signatures, and flag-handling synchronization in IMAP Object ID Bis. 

